WEBVTT

00:00.634 --> 00:03.101
(UPBEAT PIANO MUSIC)

00:03.170 --> 00:05.937
♪♪♪

00:06.006 --> 00:08.941
(INDISTINCT SPEAKING)

00:12.646 --> 00:15.380
- Let me help you, Momma.
- I don't need any help.

00:15.449 --> 00:18.383
I give God thanks I made it here
alive in this death trap.

00:18.452 --> 00:20.786
- I barely hit the accelerator.

00:20.854 --> 00:23.722
- All hours of the night you and
Frankie running around doing what?

00:23.791 --> 00:26.291
- We've been through this.
- That's how detectives work.

00:26.359 --> 00:29.127
- Well, the only work
you are doing today

00:29.196 --> 00:31.797
- is to worship the Lord.
- Hard labour.

00:31.799 --> 00:34.599
- I heard that.

00:34.668 --> 00:37.202
- God wants to work a miracle

00:37.270 --> 00:39.204
in your life today.

00:39.206 --> 00:42.274
- (WOMAN): Yes, he does!
- To renew you...

00:42.342 --> 00:44.142
- and make you whole again.
- (MAN): Praise Jesus!

00:44.211 --> 00:46.144
- Our Lord says, "I am the Lord

00:46.147 --> 00:48.347
that healeth thee."

00:48.415 --> 00:51.216
- Can I hear an amen?
- (ALL): Amen!

00:51.218 --> 00:54.219
- (LOUDER): I said, "Can I hear
an amen?" - (ALL, LOUDER): Amen!

00:54.288 --> 00:56.121
- "In my name, they shall

00:56.189 --> 00:58.090
cast out devils."
- (WOMAN): Yes, Father!

00:58.158 --> 01:00.492
- "They shall speak
in new tongues."

01:00.494 --> 01:02.994
- Glory to God in the highest!
- "They shall take up serpents

01:03.063 --> 01:05.230
"that shall not hurt them.

01:05.299 --> 01:08.300
And they shall lay hands on the sick."

01:08.368 --> 01:11.603
- (WOMAN): Preach!
- "And they shall recover."

01:11.671 --> 01:14.573
- Can I hear a hallelujah?
- (ALL): Hallelujah!

01:14.641 --> 01:17.876
- God has sent us
his anointed healer...

01:17.944 --> 01:20.112
- (MAN): Preach!
- ...to raise us up out

01:20.114 --> 01:22.247
from the Valley of the Dry Bones.

01:22.315 --> 01:25.784
Brothers and sisters, Elsie Thompson!

01:25.852 --> 01:28.019
(APPLAUSE)

01:28.088 --> 01:30.589
- She's so young.
- David was but

01:30.657 --> 01:32.424
a child when he flung that stone.

01:34.895 --> 01:36.661
I better join that line now

01:36.664 --> 01:39.131
if I want my aching hip
to receive healing.

01:39.199 --> 01:42.467
(VIOLIN MUSIC)

01:42.536 --> 01:45.370
♪♪♪

